column2: The Easter Bunny has awoken from a long rest!
The Easter Bunny checks the time and confirms it's Easter Eve. Time to wake up and get ready!
The Easter Bunny does some stretches after waking up!
The Easter Bunny opens up his laptop to check the latest news.
The Easter Bunny checks for any last-minute basket requests.
The Easter Bunny sends off the last-minute basket requests to the Basket Wrapping Center.
The Easter Bunny is busy in the kitchen making a hearty breakfast!
The Easter Bunny sits on the patio enjoying the nice views while eating breakfast.
The Easter Bunny's meteorologists start gearing up to begin final weather checks.
The Easter Bunny's meteorologists head outside to get the latest weather report.
The Easter Bunny receives a call from Santa Claus wishing the Easter Bunny all the best for the journey ahead!
The Easter Bunny is still chatting with Santa Claus discussing clever places to hide eggs!
The Easter Bunny's meteorologists complete final weather checks. Wind is calm skies are clear and the weather is looking good!
The Easter Bunny gets ready to head to the workshop to start final basket checks!
On the way to the workshop the Easter Bunny chats with all the Easter Bunny's helpers thanking them for their hard work this year.
After a lovely chat with the Easter Bunny's helpers the Easter Bunny starts heading to the workshop!
The Easter Bunny starts final basket checks making sure that not a single egg is cracked!
Final basket checks are underway. So far zero cracked eggs have been found!
Final basket checks have been completed with the Easter Bunny certifying there are zero cracked eggs!
The Easter Bunny starts heading out of the workshop and is on the way to the Easter Bunny Cafe!
The Easter Bunny sits down for a quick coffee and catches up on the latest Easter Island news.
While at the cafe the paparazzi stops by for a moment to get some photos of the Easter Bunny before departure.
The Easter Bunny's geographers start final route checks ensuring the Easter Bunny can travel the globe in a day!
The Easter Bunny has left the cafe but we can't seem to figure out where the Easter Bunny is going next...
In the meantime the Easter Bunny's helpers start wrapping the last batch of baskets in preparation for liftoff!
Oh my! We've spotted the Easter Bunny at the arcade that's definitely not in the plans for preparations.
We can confirm the Easter Bunny is winning quite a lot of games and getting a lot of tickets.
After quite the arcade session the Easter Bunny redeems his tickets for...a plush Easter Bunny.
With the Easter Bunny plush in hand the Easter Bunny sits down with the geographers to look at the route.
The Easter Bunny suggests a few changes to the route to ensure the most optimal path!
After studying the route the Easter Bunny gives two thumbs up saying the route looks great!
With the route set the Easter Bunny heads back home to grab the baskets for liftoff!
The Easter Bunny starts packing the baskets into the sleigh making sure they're all snug and secure.
All baskets are packed and ready to go! The Easter Bunny double-checks to ensure nothing's been forgotten.
With everything set the Easter Bunny prepares to take off on this year's Easter journey!
And they're off! The Easter Bunny and the Easter Bunny's helpers are now officially on their way for Easter 2024!
mohammed  boulaich el habate ksar sghir
